ource closest to?</label></input><input ref="/water/id"><label>Please enter pre-existing ID number for this water point, if any.</label><hint>Write none if there is no pre-existing ID number.</hint></input><select1 ref="/water/type"><label>What kind of water scheme/source is it?</label><item><label>Rainwater harvesting scheme</label><value>rainwater</value></item><item><label>Developed / protected spring water</label><value>spring_water</value></item><item><label>Tube well</label><value>tube_well</value></item><item><label>Protected dug well</label><value>dug_well</value></item><item><label>Developed and treated surface water</label><value>surface_water</value></item><item><label>Borehole</label><value>borehole</value></item><item><label>Other</label><value>other</value></item></select1><input ref="/water/type_other"><label>Please specify</label></input><select1 ref="/water/distribution_type"><label>What is the type of distribution of the water scheme/source?</label><item><label>Single point (where the scheme is located)</label><value>single_point</value></item><item><label>Mulitple points less than 100m reticulation</label><value>multiple_points_100m_reticulation</value></item><item><label>Multiple points more than 1km reticulation</label><value>multiple_points_&gt;1km_reticulation</value></item><item><label>Multiple points less than 1km reticulation</label><value>multiple_points_&lt;1km_reticulation</value></item></select1><select1 ref="/water/lift_mechanism"><label>What is the lift mechanism?</label><item><label>Hand pump</label><value>hand_pump</value></item><item><label>Rope/pulley</label><value>rope_and_pulley</value></item><item><label>Other</label><value>other</value></item><item><label>Animal powered pump</label><value>animal_powered_pump</value></item><item><label>Solar pump</label><value>solar_pump</value></item><item><label>Electric motor pump</label><value>electric_motor_pump</value></item><item><label>Don't know</label><value>not_known</value></item><i