_community"><label>Please specify the name of the managing entity from Community.</label></input><input ref="/water/manager_private_org"><label>Please specify the name of the managing entity from Private organization.</label></input><input ref="/water/manager_state_govt"><label>Please specify the name of the managing entity from State government.</label></input><input ref="/water/manager_other"><label>Please specify the name of the managing entity from Other.</label></input><input ref="/water/manager_local_govt"><label>Please specify the name of the managing entity from Local government.</label></input><select1 ref="/water/pay_for_water"><label>Do people have to pay for water from this water source/scheme?</label><item><label>Yes</label><value>yes</value></item><item><label>No</label><value>no</value></item></select1><select1 ref="/water/used_today"><label>Does it appear that this water source/scheme has been used today?</label><item><label>Yes</label><value>yes</value></item><item><label>No</label><value>no</value></item></select1><select1 ref="/water/not_used_pump_broken"><label>Is this water source/scheme not in use because the pump mechanism broken?</label><item><label>Yes</label><value>yes</value></item><item><label>Don't Know</label><value>dont_know</value></item><item><label>No</label><value>no</value></item></select1><select1 ref="/water/not_used_no_diesel"><label>Is this water source/scheme not in use because there is no diesel to run the pump?</label><item><label>Yes</label><value>yes</value></item><item><label>Don't Know</label><value>dont_know</value></item><item><label>No</label><value>no</value></item></select1><select1 ref="/water/not_used_point_broken"><label>Is this water source/scheme not in use because the kiosk, tap or tank is broken?</label><item><label>Yes</label><value>yes</value></item><item><label>Don't Know</label><value>dont_know</value></item><item><label>No</label><value>no</value></item></select1><select1 ref="/water/not_used_poor_water